    "description": "WELL PANEL is a completely wireless, IP65-rated, battery-powered wash light with 24 quad-color LEDs. The robust unit delivers bright, fully saturate tones and pastel colors, casting it as the right tool for onstage productions or highlighting scenic and architectural pieces. Adjustable beam angles and the included magnetic diffuser adds even wider coverage. This truly versatile fixture is capable of selectable dimming, red shift emulation, and PWM settings. Control your way via W-DMX, DMX.",
